description: The quake kills at least nine in eastern Turkey, with injuries and collapsed buildings in Iran.
title: Earthquake kills at least 9 in Turkey, injures many in Iran
title_page: Earthquake kills at least 9 in Turkey, injures many in Iran - BBC News
maintext: Last month two avalanches in Van province killed at least 39 people including rescue workers, while in the provinces of Elazig and Malatya at least 31 people died and more than 1,600 injured in a powerful quake.
